comments.body: Mech ki 5 seats Khali h woh shyd , ECE agar lucky hue toh
Tech branch toh Milne se rhi , bacha ECE lekin usme bhi 15 hi seats h . Jyada hopes Mt rkho par councelling attend krne me koi harm ni h kal .
Mai ab SRM me CSE w/s Cloud Computing ka branch me hun. Is ECE at PES better than what I'm studying rn?

Depends apka interest electronics me h ki ni. I don't think so ECE at pes is better than SRM CSE , considering curriculum tough hoga , Placements ke bare me rant karte dekha hai logo ko issi sub pe etc. Although I heard that we can change branch if we have good CGPA ( idk howmuch ) so it's your call.. Wouldn't recommend to sacrifice your branch and interests. But do attend councelling tomorrow:)
And I hope ktr wala campus hoga ?
